VYHY DBUr-YHVH 'aLY L'aMUr.
BN-'aDM HNB'a 'aL-NBY'aY YShUr'aL HNB'aYM V'aMUrTh LNBY'aY MLBM ShM'yV DBUr- YHVH.
KH 'aMUr 'aDNY YHVH HVY 'yL-HNBY'aYM HNBLYM 'aShUr HLKYM 'aChUr UrVChM VLBLThY Ur'aV.
KSh'yLYM BChUrBVTh NBY'aYK YShUr'aL HYV.
L'a 'yLYThM BPhUrTShVTh VThGDUrV GDUr 'yL-BYTh YShUr'aL L'yMD BMLChMH BYVM YHVH.
ChZV ShV'a VQSM KZB H'aMUrYM N'aM-YHVH VYHVH L'a ShLChM VYChLV LQYM DBUr.
HLV'a MChZH-ShV'a ChZYThM VMQSM KZB 'aMUrThM V'aMUrYM N'aM-YHVH V'aNY L'a DBUrThY.
LKN KH 'aMUr 'aDNY YHVH Y'yN DBUrKM ShV'a VChZYThM KZB LKN HNNY 'aLYKM N'aM 'aDNY YHVH.
VHYThH YDY 'aL-HNBY'aYM HChZYM ShV'a VHQSMYM KZB BSVD 'yMY L'a-YHYV VBKThB BYTh-YShUr'aL L'a YKThBV V'aL-'aDMTh YShUr'aL L'a YB'aV VYD'yThM KY 'aNY 'aDNY YHVH.
Y'yN VBY'yN HT'yV 'aTh-'yMY L'aMUr ShLVM V'aYN ShLVM VHV'a BNH ChYTSh VHNM TChYM 'aThV ThPhL.
'aMUr 'aL-TChY ThPhL VYPhL HYH GShM ShVTPh V'aThNH 'aBNY 'aLGBYSh ThPhLNH VUrVCh S'yUrVTh ThBQ'y.
VHNH NPhL HQYUr HLV'a Y'aMUr 'aLYKM 'aYH HTYCh 'aShUr TChThM.
LKN KH 'aMUr 'aDNY YHVH VBQ'yThY UrVCh-S'yUrVTh BChMThY VGShM ShTPh B'aPhY YHYH V'aBNY 'aLGBYSh BChMH LKLH.
VHUrSThY 'aTh-HQYUr 'aShUr-TChThM ThPhL VHG'yThYHV 'aL-H'aUrTSh VNGLH YSDV VNPhLH VKLYThM BThVKH VYD'yThM KY-'aNY YHVH.
VKLYThY 'aTh-ChMThY BQYUr VBTChYM 'aThV ThPhL V'aMUr LKM 'aYN HQYUr V'aYN HTChYM 'aThV.
NBY'aY YShUr'aL HNB'aYM 'aL-YUrVShLM VHChZYM LH ChZVN ShLM V'aYN ShLM N'aM 'aDNY YHVH.
V'aThH BN-'aDM ShYM PhNYK 'aL-BNVTh 'yMK HMThNB'aVTh MLBHN VHNB'a 'yLYHN.
V'aMUrTh KH-'aMUr 'aDNY YHVH HVY LMThPhUrVTh KSThVTh 'yL KL-'aTShYLY YDY V'yShVTh HMSPhChVTh 'yL-Ur'aSh KL-QVMH LTShVDD NPhShVTh HNPhShVTh ThTShVDDNH L'yMY VNPhShVTh LKNH ThChYYNH.
VThChLLNH 'aThY 'aL-'yMY BSh'yLY Sh'yUrYM VBPhThVThY LChM LHMYTh NPhShVTh 'aShUr L'a-ThMVThNH VLChYVTh NPhShVTh 'aShUr L'a-ThChYYNH BKZBKM L'yMY ShM'yY KZB.
LKN KH-'aMUr 'aDNY YHVH HNNY 'aL-KSThVThYKNH 'aShUr 'aThNH MTShDDVTh ShM 'aTh- HNPhShVTh LPhUrChVTh VQUr'yThY 'aThM M'yL ZUrV'yThYKM VShLChThY 'aTh-HNPhShVTh 'aShUr 'aThM MTShDDVTh 'aTh-NPhShYM LPhUrChTh.
VQUr'yThY 'aTh-MSPhChThYKM VHTShLThY 'aTh-'yMY MYDKN VL'a-YHYV 'yVD BYDKN LMTShVDH VYD'yThN KY-'aNY YHVH.
Y'yN HK'aVTh LB-TShDYQ ShQUr V'aNY L'a HK'aBThYV VLChZQ YDY UrSh'y LBLThY- ShVB MDUrKV HUr'y LHChYThV.
LKN ShV'a L'a ThChZYNH VQSM L'a-ThQSMNH 'yVD VHTShLThY 'aTh-'yMY MYDKN VYD'yThN KY-'aNY YHVH.
